44:20.705 --> 44:23.257
you wanna leave your car
if you're feeling light-headed?

44:25.927 --> 44:27.929
probably should.

44:27.929 --> 44:29.881
what'll i say
if somebody calls?

44:29.881 --> 44:33.601
you tell 'em we'll talk 5:00
tomorrow in person,
or one of those things'll...

44:33.601 --> 44:37.221
get shoved in his belly
or get shoved up his ass,
and we'll see if it works.

44:37.221 --> 44:41.442
- see if his ass works?
- you wanna get clever
  on me, you, huh?

44:41.442 --> 44:44.312
i'm really dizzy, jimmy.
i'm gonna wind
your watch up, pal.

44:44.312 --> 44:46.564
come on, jimmy.

44:46.564 --> 44:48.866
you okay, mouse? huh?
we should go.

44:49.367 --> 44:52.620
all right. let's go to
chez liery. i'll straighten
you right out, okay?

44:52.620 --> 44:56.824
-yeah.
